sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Helper as Direct MCP stdio helper
    participant MCP as VsMcpBridge.McpServer
    participant VsTools as VsTools.bridge_regex_text_search
    participant Executor as BridgeToolExecutor
    participant Catalog as IBridgeToolCatalog
    participant Tool as RegexTextSearchTool
    participant Audit as IAuditSink

    Helper->>MCP: initialize
    MCP-->>Helper: VsMcpBridge.McpServer 1.0.0.0
    Helper->>MCP: tools/list
    MCP-->>Helper: 18 tools including bridge_regex_text_search
    Helper->>VsTools: tools/call bridge_regex_text_search(pattern, entries, maxResults)
    VsTools->>Executor: ExecuteAsync(BridgeToolRequest: bridge.regexTextSearch)
    Executor->>Catalog: TryGetTool("bridge.regexTextSearch")
    Catalog-->>Executor: RegexTextSearchTool descriptor
    Executor->>Executor: policy, approval, secret-reference checks
    Executor->>Tool: ExecuteAsync(request)
    Tool-->>Executor: BridgeToolResult success with limited matches
    Executor->>Audit: RecordAsync(BridgeAuditEnvelope)
    Executor-->>VsTools: BridgeToolResult with requestId and operationId
    VsTools-->>Helper: JSON result

    Helper->>VsTools: tools/call bridge_regex_text_search(invalid pattern)
    VsTools->>Executor: ExecuteAsync(BridgeToolRequest: bridge.regexTextSearch)
    Executor->>Tool: ExecuteAsync(request)
    Tool-->>Executor: BridgeToolResult InvalidRegex
    Executor->>Audit: RecordAsync(BridgeAuditEnvelope)
    Executor-->>VsTools: structured failure
    VsTools-->>Helper: JSON result with errorCode InvalidRegex
